    {
      "id": "z4Ij_0uNJFFgNSdyffJHp",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 422.2666664123535,
      "y": 1557.5,
      "width": 148,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b06",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 222773971,
      "version": 242,
      "versionNonce": 109757743,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1739637169593,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "2. Write to DB",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "2. Write to DB",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "urjj46WTXgBrNQa6APazR",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 52,
      "y": 2040,
      "width": 1185.5999755859375,
      "height": 225,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b08",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 309889459,
      "version": 633,
      "versionNonce": 273852737,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1739637169593,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Pros \n1. Enough confidence via the metrics to understand the data transfered between existing and new architecture is similar.\n2. Strongly consistent data is being maintained \n\n\n\nCons\n1. Write latency to local DB has increased (both systems need to write)\n2. We have to invest in conflict resolution in 2 places (1 in Journal Service and 1 in the replication entry old mechanism)",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Pros \n1. Enough confidence via the metrics to understand the data transfered between existing and new architecture is similar.\n2. Strongly consistent data is being maintained \n\n\n\nCons\n1. Write latency to local DB has increased (both systems need to write)\n2. We have to invest in conflict resolution in 2 places (1 in Journal Service and 1 in the replication entry old mechanism)",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "LZJcioKsqGacahr2bf4Zd",
      "type": "text",
